        public static ListTools.SeriesList createSeriesList​(String leader,
                                                    String trailer,
                                                    int size)
        Create a new SeriesList with the given leader, trailer and size.
        Parameters:
        leader - the String that will prefix the index
        trailer - the String that will suffix the index
        size - the length of the list
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if leader or trailer are null (use the empty string instead)
        IllegalArgumentException - if the size is negative
